MADONNA Body Of Evidence (Rare original 1992 US MGM promotional only press pack for the movie starring Madonna, Willem Dafoe, Joe Mantegna and Anne Archer. Comprises a 32-page booklet featuring credits, film production details and informationon the cast and crew. Also includes fourteen 8" x 10" glossy MGM black & white publicity photographs of film stills - seven of which feature Madonna. Housed in a custom Maddy & Willem colour picture folder. The folder has a small tear and some lightstorage wear, otherwise the contents are near mint - a stunning Madonna movie collectable)
